track_notes: 30/03/13 - Although out of the Scottish SOTA Winter Bonus period this route was still in winter condition. Use of snow-shoes or cross country skis would have been helpful. On the return journey heading up Lairig Dhoirean NN161344 the surrounding slopes had a high avalanche potential. (On the same day a skier had died in an avalanche in Glencoe) Careful choice had to be made as to the safest slope. The Track-Back shows the slope I chose.
